    "At Bonn Bandmann published his <em>habilitationsschrift</em>, the groundbreaking <em>Mittelalterliche Architektur als Bedeutungstr\u00e4ger</em> (Medieval Architecture as a Bearer of Meaning), a work which would become a classic in the field.": [
