    "Bandmann drew on the historical circumstances and social factors (<em>Zeitm\u00e4chten</em>) of the middle ages to create a new criteria for architectural history, most influentially seen in his <em>Mittelalterliche Architektur als Bedeutungstr\u00e4ger</em>.": [
